{"tid":1559879,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"唔好忘記畫家","createTime":"2019-09-11T04:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T04:36:17.000Z","uid":31907,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a7b209d4a038fd63f35da521bd1ed78c5b419c63","tid":1559879,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:02:40.000Z","msg":"今日 11:25 時事脈搏<br />\n涉圍警總佔旺畫家還押候審<br />\n <br />\n放大圖片<br />\n外號「佔旺畫家」的31歲男子潘浩超，涉嫌參與6.21圍灣仔警察總部，經控方申請修改控罪後，被控‬1項參與未經批准集結、1項刑毀和7項襲警等罪，在東區裁判法院再提訊。<br />\n<br />\n控方要求將案件押後至本月25日，又指事態有新發現，警方現時懷疑「畫家」或牽涉其他案件，雖然涉事日子與本案不同，但相關證據顯示有些關連性。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官批准案件押後，指他在其他案件保釋期間犯案，而且控罪嚴重，拒絕保釋申請，被告須還押監房。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/09/11/2247671_675b6204297529ab33bb93b6f770bde7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F09%2F11%2F2247671_675b6204297529ab33bb93b6f770bde7.jpg&h=801fe9db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74f3d09fb3062e6519fb717038919cf9d866f27d","tid":1559879,"uid":185788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:06:22.000Z","msg":"畫家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d23bbd733b524da12bb39bc31b55ae855910241","tid":1559879,"uid":26441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:11:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"414ba7d7d625c239786b35cb9c5cd20c426448d5","tid":1559879,"uid":152584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:15:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfbcd67ab57763cd755e4942b577f96c8a0f9883","tid":1559879,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:18:04.000Z","msg":"畫家唔比保釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /